<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VoxView - Data Visualization & Viewpoint Analysis</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7f00ff, #e100ff);
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 120px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: block;
            z-index: 1;
            position: relative;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #0c0202;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        h4 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        main {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        button {
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8e2de2, #4a00e0);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, background 0.3s ease;
            z-index: 1;
            position: relative;
        }

        button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a00e0, #8e2de2);
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <img src="../VoxView.png" alt="VoxView Logo" class="logo">
            <h1>Welcome to VoxView!</h1>
            <h4>Decoding Debate, Defining Discourse</h4>
        </header>
        <main>
            <h2>Hello, User!</h2>
            <p>We are delighted to have you here. Explore our website to discover more about what we offer in data visualization and viewpoint analysis.</p>
            <button>Learn More</button>
        </main>
        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2024 VoxView. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
